OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FFamilies of children with cancer who
OL,8,Fcontracted infections at the Queen
OL,9,FElizabeth University Hospital (QEUH)
OL,10,Fin Glasgow have met with the
OL,11,FScotland's First Minister.
OL,13,FCharly Bisset from Peebles was being
OL,14,Ftreated for Leukaemia at the QEUH in
OL,15,F2019 when she caught a viral infection
OL,16,Fand was treated for aspergillosis, an
OL,17,Fillness caused by breathing in small
OL,18,Famounts of mould.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FThe QEUH, coined Glasgow's 'super
OL,8,Fhospital,' opened in 2015 and has been
OL,9,Fplagued by a long running controversy
OL,10,Fover contaminated water and
OL,11,Fventilation systems.
OL,13,FCharly was treated for leukaemia in
OL,14,Fthe adult wards in 2019 after
OL,15,Finfections meant the children's cancer
OL,16,Fwards were closed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,FHer family believe the medication she
OL,8,Fwas given to treat aspergillosis, and
OL,9,Fthe length of time she was given it,
OL,10,Fled to Charly developing adrenal
OL,11,Fsufficiency which means she can't
OL,12,Fproduce adrenaline or other essential
OL,13,Fhormones and needs to carry medication
OL,14,Fwith her at all times.
OL,16,FCharley said: "I hate it, I hate
OL,17,Fcarrying about my injection, I hate it.
OL,19,F"It just doesn't make me feel normal.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"I can't go out alone, I can't do
OL,8,Fanything alone, I can't stay home
OL,9,Falone - someone needs to be with me at
OL,10,Fall times."
OL,12,FOn Thursday First Minister John
OL,13,FSwinney met with families affected
OL,14,Fover a video call.
OL,16,FHe said: "I was grateful to meet with
OL,17,Ffamilies impacted by the Queen
OL,18,FElizabeth University Inquiry and am
OL,19,Fgrateful for their time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"I want to again recognise the
OL,8,Fprofound, unimaginable pain and loss
OL,9,Fthey have experienced, and I
OL,10,Fappreciate the inquiry has reopened
OL,11,Flongstanding and deeply painful wounds.
OL,13,F"I welcomed the engagement and
OL,14,Fappreciated the candour and views
OL,15,Fexpressed by them during our meeting.
OL,17,F"I made clear that today is the start
OL,18,Fof a wider discussion with the
OL,19,FGovernment to help families get the
OL,20,Fanswers they need.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"We will continue to do everything in
OL,8,Four power to help them get the answers
OL,9,Fthey rightly deserve, and families
OL,10,Fwill have an important part to play in
OL,11,Fthe new Safety and Public Confidence
OL,12,FOversight Group."
OL,14,FCharly's Dad Mark Bisset said: "I feel
OL,15,Fhe was listening, he was sympathetic
OL,16,Fto what we were saying but politically
OL,17,Fhe's tied.
OL,19,F"It's always been about the truth, and
OL,20,Fapologies.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1773004306
OL,3,CFamilies meet with Scottish First
OL,4,CMinister over hospital infection
OL,5,Cscandal
OL,7,F"There's too many people getting away
OL,8,Fwith what's happened until now; a lot
OL,9,Fof those responsible are retiring with
OL,10,Fa golden handshake, whereas our kids
OL,11,Fhave been left behind with serious
OL,12,Fconsequences."
OL,14,FA public inquiry into the construction
OL,15,Fof the QEUH was held earlier this year
OL,16,Fand is expected to report back on its
OL,17,Ffindings before 2027, but it is not
OL,18,Fexpected to examine the consequences
OL,19,Fof the anti-fungal medication and long
OL,20,Fterm symptoms patients are now living
OL,21,Fwith.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/7
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
